conventions are
over, has invariably won the
popular vote.

20:44.910 --> 20:48.114 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, you're getting to a point
where the election
starts to get cooked.

20:48.147 --> 20:54.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's not quite baked yet, but it
is like concrete
getting set, getting harder and
harder.

20:54.420 --> 21:00.226 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it takes -- it takes more
and more power
to change what's been laid as
you go forward.

21:00.259 --> 21:03.462 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is really -- even though
we're still
in the summer, we're still in
August, this

21:03.496 --> 21:06.532 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
