changed a little bit since Mitt
Romney and

21:24.416 --> 21:26.785 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
John McCain ran.

21:26.819 --> 21:31.457 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In a state like Georgia, where
